Commented on #116 AppImage fails to open

Sooo, apparently after checking some posts on internet as I also encountered exact issue with another Tauri-based app, the only workaround to resolve this is by appending WEBKIT_DISABLE_DMABUF_RENDERER=1 var before the command in Terminal. Most likely because some issue with webkitgtk + NVIDIA combo, see https://www.reddit.com/r/tauri/comments/16tzsi8/tauri_desktop_app_not_rendering_but_web_does/ and https://github.com/wailsapp/wails/issues/2977#issuecomment-1761765185
